{"tid":485673,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"(求救)買左個WD my book","createTime":"2017-12-01T06:49:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T16:45:39.000Z","uid":32782,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0d439afc8b935549243151f5645202ea8602a14b","tid":485673,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T06:49:08.000Z","msg":"買左個4TB WD my book比部mac做back up<br />\nFormat左去HFS+J之後run Time Machine<br />\n開頭backup頭幾十gb都好地地 之後去左百幾gb開始就顯示為read only.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/01/144650_c49ab035032a31a453b424ec85431056.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F01%2F144650_c49ab035032a31a453b424ec85431056.jpg&h=4a1752ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下可以點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 部老爺mac行緊OS X EI Capitan 10.11.12<br />\n<br />\n跟哂WD同Apple Mac support來做都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c6a226f4e947b933035cd9ad3d0fddc050b0395","tid":485673,"uid":7452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T07:03:07.000Z","msg":"已死  鬼叫你買WD"},{"pid":"ab38b0f4a42c51b2c2fa396453d009365ed2891d","tid":485673,"uid":14476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T07:05:53.000Z","msg":"同你講，所有外置硬碟都係垃圾，如果係珍貴數據，請用NAS raid backup"},{"pid":"53445af754e37cbbc28ec314dfd5cfe1a62ce911","tid":485673,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T07:08:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已死  鬼叫你買WD</blockquote><br />\n咁仲有無得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5443dedd7f1c24830fbaa0b0259ec91a258bd4d","tid":485673,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T07:11:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同你講，所有外置硬碟都係垃圾，如果係珍貴數據，請用NAS raid backup</blockquote><br />\n屋企用啫，唔洗用到咁勁"},{"pid":"875eebd8fc3ed82e50ee2e34843d5d5558aeb9d6","tid":485673,"uid":3